\c 12
\s Marudzi ane gumi anotsaura
\s Jerobhoamu kuva mambo wavo
\v 1 Zvino Rehobhoamu wakaenda Shekemu, nokuti vaIsiraeri vose vakanga vaungana naShekemu kuzo- muita mambo.
\v 2 Zvino Jerobhoamu mwa- nakomana waNebhati, wakati achizvi- nzwa, (nokuti wakanga achiri Ijipiti kwaakanga atizira nokuda kwaSoromoni, Jerobhoamu akagara Ijipiti,
\v 3 vakatuma nhume kundomudana;) Jerobhoamu neu- ngano yose yavaIsiraeri vakasvika vaka- taura naRehobhoamu, vakati,
\v 4 "Baba ve- nyu vakatitakudza joko rinogozha; naizvozvo zvino imi chirerutsai basa rababa venyu rakanga richigozha; nejoko ravo rinorema ravakaisa pamusoro pedu, tigokushumirai."
\p
\v 5 Iye akati kwavari, "Chimboendai henyu, mugare mazuva matatu, mugo- dzokera kwandiri." Vanhu vakaenda.
\v 6 Ipapo mambo Rehobhoamu akarangana navakuru, vaimira pamberi paSoromoni baba vake, vachiri vapenyu akati, "Mungandipa zano reiko, randingapindura vanhu ava naro?"
\p
\v 7 Ivo vakataura kwaari vakati, "Kana mukatenda kuva muranda wava- nhu ava nhasi, mukavashumira, muka- vapindura nokutaura mashoko akanaka
\s kwavari, ipapo vachava varanda venyu
\s nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 8 Asi iye wakaramba zano ravakuru ravakanga vamupa, akarangana namajaya ezero rake, aimira pamberi pake.
\v 9 Akati kwavari, "Imi mungandipa zano reiko, ratingapindura naro vanhu ava vakataura neni, vachiti, Rerusai joko rakaiswa pamusoro pedu nababa venyu?'
\p
\v 10 Zvino majaya ezero rake akataura kwaari achiti, "Iti kuvanhu ava vakataura newe vachiti, Baba venyu vakatitakudza joko rinogozha, asi imi chitirerusirai iro,' utaure kwavari uti, Munwe wangu mu- duku mukobvu kupfuura chiuno chababa vangu.
\v 11 Zvino, baba vangu zvavakaku- takudzai joko rinorema, ini ndichawe- dzera pajoko renyu, baba vangu vaikuro- vai neshamhu; asi ini ndichakurovai nezvinyavada."
\p
\v 12 Naizvozvo Jerobhoamu navanhu vose vakasvika kuRehobhoamu nomusi wetatu, sezvavakanga varairwa nama- mbo, achiti, "Dzokeraizve kwandiri no- musi wetatu."
\v 13 Mambo akapindura va- nhu nehasha, akarasha zano ravakuru, ravakanga vamupa;
\v 14 akataura kwavari sezvaakanga apiwa zano namaj aya, akati, "Baba vangu vakakutakudzai joko rinorema, asi ini ndichawedzera pajoko renyu; baba vangu vaikurovai nasha- mhu, asi ini ndichakurovai nezvinya- vada."
\v 15 Naizvozvo mambo haana ku- teerera vanhu; nokuti chinhu icho chakanga chabva kuna Jehovha, kuti Jehovha asimbise shoko rake, raakataura naAhija muShiro kuna Jerobhoamu mwanakomana waNebhati.
\p
\v 16 Zvino vaIsiraeri vose vakati va- chiona kuti mambo haana kuvateerera, vanhu vakapindura mambo vakati, "Ti- nomugove weiko kuna Dhavhidhi? Uye hatine nhaka kumwanakomana waJese; endai kumatende enyu, vaIsiraeri; iwe Dhavhidhi, chitarira hako imba yako." Naizvozvo vaIsiraeri vakaenda kumate- nde avo.
\v 17 Asi kana vari vana vaIsiraeri, vakanga vagere mumaguta aJudha, Reho- bhoamu wakanga ari mambo wavo.
\p
\v 18 Zvino mambo Rehobhoamu aka- tuma Adhoramu mutariri wavanhu ve- chibharo, vaIsiraeri vose vakamutaka namabwe, akafa. Ipapo mambo Rehobhoamu akakurumidza kukwira ngoro yake, akatizira Jerusaremu.
\p
\v 19 Saizvozvo vaIsiraeri vakamukira
\s imba yaDhavhidhi kusvikira zuva nhasi.
\p
\v 20 Zvino vaIsiraeri vose vakati vachinzwa kuti Jerobhoamu wadzoka, vakatuma nhume kuzomudanira kuungano, vakamuita mambo wavaIsiraeri vose; hakuna wakatevera imba yaDhavhidhi, asi rudzi rwaJudha bedzi.
\p
\v 21 Zvino Rehobhoamu wakati achisvika Jerusaremu, akaunganidza vose veimba yaJudha, novorudzi rwaBhenjamini, varume vakatsaurwa vaiva nezviuru zvine zana namakumi masere, vaigona kurwa, kuzorwa neimba yaIsiraeri, kuti vadzoserezve ushe kuna Rehobhoamu mwanakomana waSoromoni.
\p
\v 22 Asi shoko raMwari rakasvika kuna Shemaya munhu waMwari richiti,
\p
\v 23 Taura naRehobhoamu mwanakomana waSoromoni, mambo wavaJudha, nokuimba yose yaJudha neyaBhenjamini, nokuna vamwe vanhu, uti,
\v 24 "Zvanzi naJehovha, Hamufaniri kukwira kundorwa nehama dzenyu ivo vana vaIsiraeri; mumwe nomumwe ngaadzokere kumba kwake, nokuti chinhu ichi chinobva kwandiri." Naizvozvo vakateerera shoko raJehovha, vakadzoka, vakaenda havo, sezvavakaudzwa naJehovha.
\p
\v 25 Ipapo Jerobhoamu wakavaka Shekemu panyika yamakomo yaEfuremu, akagaramo; akabvapo, akandovaka Penueri.
\v 26 Jerobhoamu akati mumwoyo mwake, "Zvino ushe huchadzokerazve kuimba yaDhavhidhi.
\v 27 Kana vanhu ava vakakwira kundobayira zvibayiro zvavo mumba maJehovha paJerusaremu, ipapo mwoyo yavanhu ava ichadzokera kunashe wavo, iye Rehobhoamu mambo waJudha; vachindiuraya, vakadzokera kuna Rehobhoamu mambo waJudha."
\p
\v 28 Naizvozvo mambo akarangana navakuru, akaumba mhuru mbiri dzendarama, akati kwavari, "Kukwira Jerusaremu kwava kure; tarirai, vaIsiraeri, vamwari venyu vakakubudisai panyika yeIjipiti."
\v 29 Akagadza imwe paBheteri, imwe akaiisa paDhani.
\v 30 Chinhu ichi chikava chivi, nokuti vanhu vakandonamata kwadziri idzo mbiri, kusvikira paDhani.
\v 31 Akavakawo dzimba pamatunhu akakwirira, akatora vamwe pakati pava nhu akavaita vapristi, vasati vari vavana vaRevhi.
\p
\v 32 Zvino Jerobhoamu akaraira mutambo pamwedzi worusere, nezuva regumi namashanu romwedzi, wakanga wakafanana nomutambo waiva kuvaJudha; akabayira paaritari; akaitawo saizvozvo paBheteri, akabayira mhuru dzaakaumba; akagadzawo paBheteri vapristi vamatunhu akakwirira aakaita.
\v 33 Akandobayira paaritari yaakavaka paBheteri nezuva regumi namashanu romwedzi worusere, iwo mwedzi waakafunga hake mumwoyo make; akaraira vana valsiraeri mutambo, akandobayira paaritari, akapisa zvinonhuwira.
